cs.CL, cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.GT, cs.DS

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with compositional semantics of natural language and game-theoretic semantics of sentences. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is also likely as the paper discusses modifications to the grammar category to compensate for the failure of open games to form a compact closed category. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with natural language processing and semantics. 
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is relevant as the paper builds game-theoretic semantics of sentences. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with building a category of grammatical derivations.
